_sText:
A bricked in warehouse full of boxes, navigate the maze
of tetris shaped box configurations and... well shoot
the opposite team.

The entire floor is made of floorboards, so you can hear
the enemy coming, lots of pinch points and sniper points
but all points have ways around.

Recommended settings for server, leave footsteps on as
this map would be a bitch in utter silence from the
foot department.


- DevoiD
